annotation: This UI seems to be a fitness app focused on tracking workout summaries and active calorie burn. It displays workout summaries in the form of cards and also provides achievements earned by the user. The app also has a section to track active calories burned in a day through a graph. The toolbar provides options to share the workout summary and navigate to different options within the app. The UI is designed to be responsive across different resolutions and screen sizes.
